Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:30.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:36.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:44.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:51.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:10.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:15.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:22.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:28.94,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,36 万能战舰新鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰提斯的空中战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坏蛋的船\N坏蛋的船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 先躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到会追到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是来做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是来找娜蒂亚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 这并不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若真是如此 难道我们已经被发现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收到2号舰 『机械降神』回报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『本舰发现娜蒂亚』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使借助了 尼欧皇帝陛下的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今都还未能将蔚蓝之水回收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚与尼莫可能都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 回到了久违的 塔提苏司王国遗址
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这还真是个意外的惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这还真是飞来横祸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然是溜之大吉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可是把 鹦鹉螺号击沉的怪物耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三十六计走为上策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见了 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坏蛋一个\N坏蛋一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 乖乖带着蔚蓝之水走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你这么做 你的朋友们就能保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不需要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正他一定会杀了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来你似乎还下不定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 就让你瞧瞧 如果你不肯出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们会有什么下场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 我给你60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就用这些时间和朋友道别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着理他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是这样下去 只会大家一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不要在这里 死得不明不白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的意思是要娜蒂亚出去是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是最好的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这个人实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下去大家都活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…\N可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我等你来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你答应放了其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就乖乖交出蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用担心 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是拥有 足以毁灭世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不会输给那些人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强一定会来救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很快就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要乖乖等我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我会等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼大人 已经把娜蒂亚公主带上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把她带过来 礼貌点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让他们也来帮我忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 先拼命冲到葛兰坦那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剩下的就到时候再说了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们也因此获得活下去的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我给你们1分钟的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们就利用这段时间 好好逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 这个小人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命\N遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们走着瞧 石像鬼\N我们走着瞧 石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有40秒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不准对公主无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是稀客 娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够再次与你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我感到无上的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是说会放过他们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这是在故意找碴喔 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经给了他们 活下去的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算是仁至义尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若你没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连同你在内的所有人 早就已经命丧黄泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得你应该要感谢我 而不是怨恨我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我之前不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要将我和那些 愚蠢的生物混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼大人 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始炮击 先从距离300公尺处开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后再以50公尺的间隔逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到了吗 娜蒂亚 我是多么地仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样等于又给了他们 更多活下去的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 我们迟早会玩完的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爆炸的声音逐渐逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他打算把我们折磨到死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没到葛兰坦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真走运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了它就等于有百倍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标的移动速度增加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是搭上了某种交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好慢喔 不能再快一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样已经是最快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟它浑身是伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方还在攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙怎么这么不死心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隧道上方恐怕撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就快点离开这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回则是快过头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度过快容易导致事故发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刹车根本不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,切换至倒车档如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有用 那样只会毁掉齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 汽缸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 只有前面的能动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙了 要是直接撞上墙壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来一切要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真走运！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有气球…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说那些五四三了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 汽缸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不够长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种高度摔下去必死无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 下面就是墓园…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒是省了一番工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是虚幻的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经撞到地面了吗？\N已经撞到地面了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我们浮在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保住一命了\N保住一命了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标和某种东西接触
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来是中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于上钩了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是谁？ 又想把我们带去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在这种情况 就算慌张也于事无补
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们被放到地面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那艘船也降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那飞机的形状好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全没有机翼 它究竟是怎么飞的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟刚才的船好像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道是新亚特兰提斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就不会出手相救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说不定是打算在这里 把我们解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我对那艘船没什么好感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么 你平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 托各位的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你们前些时日的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚…娜蒂亚被捉走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 没能及时赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们立刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 目前时候未到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须等待机会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,详情以后再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在请各位先跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长正在等候各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 他应该还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在这一带的地底 侦测到高能源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,部分遗迹似乎还在运作着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而晓得这个秘密的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有尼莫和我们组织
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他可能还在这里活得好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标进入第6区域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直相信我们会再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但没料到就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我早就知道会是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标反应在第7区域消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,推测那里存在着 可以阻断电波的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫一定就是潜伏在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 准备攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们这么做 都只是为了查出 尼莫船长他们的下落？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以为我会放过那些 没用的家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好长的隧道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底要开到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个古怪的建筑物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 那是一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在胡说什么啊 讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里可是地底耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所谓的船是指浮在水面上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我过来你们就会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座电梯居然是斜着爬升的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长\N尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里到底是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本舰的第一舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一舰桥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…我们是在船里是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是…\N你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,依可丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么现在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,详情日后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前本舰上空有两只苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 已经拍摄到 正上方的空中战舰影像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 显示到主荧幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼那家伙 已经发现本舰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 居然对我们开火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成要这样坐以待毙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船不能出动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成对消灭辅助引擎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 还动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,号称万能的这艘船 若是引擎无法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就跟濒死的狸猫没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地底的能源反应依然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,命还真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射大型歼灭炸弹\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如此一来他们绝对难逃一死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来小命是暂时保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还以为死定了呢\N我还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是好暗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我得一辈子都在 这样的黑暗中度过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,启动备用电源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们被活埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那颗炸弹的威力可真大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是再来一颗 可就大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为求谨慎再丢一颗下去好了\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尽速完成装填
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙 他打算赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船还没办法反击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成对消灭辅助引擎检测完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞轮连结准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,启动成对消灭引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备电子炮电击战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰准备电子炮电击战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,复原倾斜 抬起船身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抬起船身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连接反重力推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,推力上升 1160万吨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新鹦鹉螺号 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船是新鹦鹉螺号？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船就是万能战舰 新鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这个？ 这么破旧的遗迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是它脱胎换骨后的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成是…梦幻的遗迹战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主雷达开始运作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辅助引擎输出功率达103%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各汽缸内压力正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标 敌方空中战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一炮塔全自动射击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标 敌方空中战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,传达动力至第一炮塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敌方战舰的主炮正在转动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:18:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不快点发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,防护罩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方位瞄准仪捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自动追踪装置设定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,压力突破临界点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弹药填装完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标侦测完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,误差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上下角3度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,击落了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到它一击就打下机械降神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样的火力…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他果然让梦幻的遗迹兵器 『艾格希里昂』重现世间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本舰进入敌方炮塔轴线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼大人 敌方战舰想与您通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接过来\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见 石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说啊 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然还能再次这样和你对话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真是做梦也想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你很遗憾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我女儿应该在你那艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把她还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是你开了口 这件事也没得商量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我只好诉诸武力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你应该办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你是个 无法杀死女儿的温柔男子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果还希望你女儿活久一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就交出你的蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来尼莫船长也有蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要怎么做？尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射主炮 副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着顾虑 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我答应过娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定会去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 在娜蒂亚被石像鬼利用前 我得先解决掉他们才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 虽然多数人的性命重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也请您想想 一条生命的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托您 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼 这是我的蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有本事你就自己过来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长\N船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你的邀请 不过 看来没那个必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成…是尼欧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧在船上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次承蒙尼欧皇帝陛下 亲自驾临
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧皇帝的力量 应该没有强到这种地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在才对尼欧皇帝的力量 感到惊讶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皇帝不可能永远都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再加上我方还拥有 优秀的科学力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他利用机械 增幅尼欧的念波是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么一来连船长都赢不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵照约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已经将蔚蓝之水交了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我答应保住娜蒂亚的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就再会了 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,旧塔提苏司已经没有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就用它来实验前些日子 挖掘出来的重力子炸弹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备发射重力子炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们就成为尼莫的墓碑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,旧塔提苏司王国
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及蓝色诺亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再会了 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:54.72,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:24:02.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:07.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:12.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:21.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:31.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.26,0:24:40.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.11,0:24:44.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:48.91,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.98,0:24:58.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.53,0:25:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧皇帝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.04,0:25:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让两颗蔚蓝之水合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.47,0:25:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和爸爸的蔚蓝之水…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.31,0:25:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 神之船『红色诺亚』 复活的时刻已经来到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.91,0:25:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚公主 让我引领你至另一艘诺亚方舟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.68,0:25:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 快来…快来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.72,0:25:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『尼欧皇帝』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.99,0:25:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敬请期待
